\c 130
\s Kuchema kwomutadzi kuna Jehovha
\d Rwiyo rworwendo.
\p
\v 1 Ndakadanidzira kwamuri, Jehovha, ndiri makadzika.
\v 2 Ishe inzwai izwi rangu; Nzeve dzenyu ngadziteerere Izwi rokukumbira kwangu.
\v 3 Dai imi Jehovha, mairangarira zvisakarurama, Ndianiko airamba amire, Ishe?
\v 4 Asi kukanganwirwa kuriko kwamuri, Kuti vanhu vakutyei.
\v 5 Ndinorindira Jehovha, mweya wangu unorindira; Ndinotarira shoko rake.
\v 6 Mweya wangu unorindira Ishe, Kupfuura varindi vanorindira rungwanani; Zvirokwazvo, kupfuura varindi vanorindira rungwanani.
\v 7 Imi Isiraeri, tarirai kuna Jehovha; .Sokuti kuna Jehovha kune ngoni, Uye kwaari kunokudzikinurwa kukuru.
\v 8 Iye achadzikinura Isiraeri Panezvisakarurama zvake zvose.
